Author: Alexs7
Title: [ANN] !!BIG BOUNTY!! Metta World's First Uberization APP For Any Offline Service
Body: Thank you very much for your question.  If you meant under the "major players" of investors, we have already had agreements  with fiat investors for long time cooperation. Speculators do not interest us, unfortunately their main majority here. If you meant tokenization off line services like a medicine or car repair then of course we do not set the immediate goal of full tokenization of all offline services. We will include tokens Metta into ecosystem of our service to use smart contracns to show the general public the benefits of decentralization.  METTA POSITIONING Growing competition in the searching engines causes constant increase in promotion costs, context advertising expenses: in this battle between the «mastodons» with million budgets there is no or little space for small businesses or start-ups. Metta project team has promoted totally 2000 businesses in 10 years of work the internet marketing area. Today we are confident to claim that a wide class of small business has formed which cannot afford to advertise in Gooogle or Yandex search engines or popular social networks. Metta primarily focuses on this target group, which has remained «out of the box» of these Internet search monopolists.

Author: Alexs7
Title: [ANN] !!BIG BOUNTY!! Metta World's First Uberization APP For Any Offline Service
Body: Thanks for the question, Here's the video ( https://youtu.be/pCMtKe2x31s ) there about some examples of services that the Metta platform offers. We will not only assure the taxi, (which has already been done), but also other markets - which are HUGE quantity.  Last week I met with the owners of large dental clinics. It is not a secret that this sphere of services is sufficiently closed and has a high margin. How many last time did you pay for the treatment of your teeth? Imagine that you can upload your x-ray pictures of teeth in Metta and send to all dentists in your location to evaluate the treatment and choose the one that suits you in terms of budget and quality. Can you do it now? Add Blockchain where this information will be stored and you will receive a project, analogues of which I have not seen here before.  Metta connects you to providers of various services directly without intermediaries - is not it great!  Why reinvent the wheel, if there are already requests from all of us to make the market cleaner? Is not this about most of the conversations here?

Author: needmoney
Title: [ANN] !!BIG BOUNTY!! Metta World's First Uberization APP For Any Offline Service
Body: BOUNTY CAMPAIGN    Web | Whitepaper | Telegram | VK | ANN Thread | Twitter | Facebook  METTA — is a platform to order offline services, gathering multiple service providers in a single application. It is a mobile solution based on geolocation and block-chain. It includes in-house currency, a system of true comments and a messenger. Metta — ordering any offline service is now as easy as calling a taxi.  Website Whitepaper  Metta platform makes the next step forward: it introduces the block-chain technology in the relation of the service provider and a customer.  It aims to: propel seller-buyer relation to a new level with equal conditions for both sides. The service quality, but not the advertising budget becomes the key factor to make a deal. Clear payment system, based on smart contracts and automatic responsibility accept guarantees reliability of the services and allows to focus on the most important aspect — obtaining high-quality services or goods for competitive market prices. to get true reviews. Only real client can comment on the service provided. The reviews will bestored in the block-chain forever. They cannot be deleted or corrected. You can always apply to the review writer with a built-in messenger. to store authentic history of the service object. For example, repair and breakdown history in the case of car repair services.  As the entry point or the initial segment, the market for car services has been selected: repair, spare parts, maintenance, sale, lease and exchange of cars and motor vehicles.  In the future we are planning to expand to such popular segments of the offline services as: medical service; renovation, rental, selling and maintenance of the real estate; repair service for home appliance, smartphones, computers, etc.;  There are  plans to propel the project into global market.  Pre-ICO Terms & Conditions   Metta tokens will be used for services payment within the platform as well as for  participation in profit distributions. SYMBOL: METTA Metta total offering size is 85 264 858 (70% including bounty). All token will be placed on exchange in two steps - pre-ICO and ICO.  Pre-ICO Offering Size   8.895.539 METTA to be sold at special Pre-ICO price.  1 342 ETH (~$432,1K)  Pre-ICO is considered successful if more than 409 ETH (~$131,5K) collected, otherwise all the funds are transferred to pre-ICO participants.  Pricing   Pre-Ico exchange rate is 1 METTA = ~0,000150 ETH (1 ETH = 6 630 METTA). ICO exchange rate is 1 METTA = 0,00027 ETH (1 ETH = 3 675 METTA).  Secure Offer   For pre-ICO METTA tokens are issued for investors only  For ICO METTA of Founders are non-transferable upon ICO completion – locked for 6 month through a smart-contract function.  Timing   ICO pre-sale Start date: 20 Nov 2017 End date: 19 Dec 2017  ICO Start date: 1 Jan 2018 End date: 1 Feb 2018   BOUNTY CAMPAIGN
